application_type_full: Outline planning permission: Some matters reserved
description: Hybrid planning application for the comprehensive, phased, redevelopment of the Grange Farm Estate: O/L application for Phases 2 and 3 comprising: Demolition of existing buildings; Erection of buildings on Plots 1 and 3 to 8 to provide 485 residential units; Community Centre (up to 1,350sqm) for D1/D2 uses within Plot 9; Community Facility (up to 282sqm) for D1 use within Plot 7.
